  "1717640": {
    "name": "Mahokenshi - The Samurai Deckbuilder",
    "steam_appid": 1717640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/0640a005904c676cc4ff5ed46594f2d1.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/c89c475f5873202b03cb50e9f91556e5.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/af76bfdb47292f407d05231738a7b558.poster.avif?t=1762953956\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/af76bfdb47292f407d05231738a7b558.webm?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/af76bfdb47292f407d05231738a7b558.mp4?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>一手挥剑，一手施法，你的天职便是保护那漂浮在天空之上的天域群岛，抵御那些试图腐化天域的强大敌人。直面命运，组建套牌，击溃敌手，完成使命。每一次游玩，你的角色都会精进几分，最终成长为世人所需的灵剑客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/5b75781857680a51b57c93976c56c4fa.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span>你将从哪里开始你的旅途？你是否来自坚韧不拔的青玉氏族？或是狡黠诡诈的黄玉氏族？还是那怒火冲天的红玉氏族？又或者是秘而不露的翠玉氏族？每个氏族都从不同的元素之灵中汲取力量，让你得以拥有不同的游玩风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/9098b74b3358703ca45cd7486d4aec14.poster.avif?t=1762953956\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/9098b74b3358703ca45cd7486d4aec14.webm?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/9098b74b3358703ca45cd7486d4aec14.mp4?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/876594c14047da1c08a5ba49fe1c47a4.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span>拥有着超过200张饱含热情的卡牌插画亟待发现。从基础套牌开始，随着你击败强敌，发掘宝藏，探寻遥远之地，选择构筑自己套牌的方向。务必步步为营，不同的地貌会带来不同的优势，因此在计划行动时必须考虑周遭的环境。在各个任务中精进你的玩法风格与策略，利用你的武士氏族优势来创造出强而有力的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/aa16fdc80cf29a1f73ae0dfe2835319e.poster.avif?t=1762953956\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/aa16fdc80cf29a1f73ae0dfe2835319e.webm?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/aa16fdc80cf29a1f73ae0dfe2835319e.mp4?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/d2955f0d20925a8263b9562f28980e9d.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span>在一系列生机勃勃、美轮美奂的3D地图中穿行。与天域群岛形形色色的人结交，拯救村庄，寻找神龛，击败嗜血的恶魔。用完全动画化的人物将你的战斗栩栩如生地展现出来。在你拯救世界的过程中施法念咒，发动暴风骤雨的攻势，展开不动如山的防守，并做出针锋相对的反击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/5c3cd4b0bff49c037d5c958886f337d9.poster.avif?t=1762953956\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/5c3cd4b0bff49c037d5c958886f337d9.webm?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/5c3cd4b0bff49c037d5c958886f337d9.mp4?t=1762953956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717640/extras/78cef09b994c274b9085ce89f2656c21.webp?t=1762953956\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们的中文讨论组，《魔法剑士》官方玩家QQ群：706721741 </p>",
